---
import { CircleCheck } from 'lucide-astro';

---
<section class="bg-[#0F2E65] py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, white 1px, transparent 0px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10"><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"><div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6"><div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] rounded-full"></div><p class="text-[#78BE20] text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Solicita tu propuesta personalizada</p></div><h2 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-6">¿Por qué escoger <span class="text-[#78BE20]">luminet</span>?</h2><p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg">Diseñamos redes robustas con monitoreo pro-activo y SLA empresariales para que tu operación nunca se detenga.</p></div><div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-white/10"><p class="text-white/90 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8">Respaldando cada conexión con tecnología, soporte y experiencia. Más que conexión, continuidad garantizada.</p><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 border border-white/5"><CircleCheck class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-[#78BE20] flex-shrink-0" /><span class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium">SLA empresarial garantizado</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 border border-white/5"><CircleCheck class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-[#78BE20] flex-shrink-0" /><span class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium">Monitoreo pro-activo 24/7</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 border border-white/5"><CircleCheck class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-[#78BE20] flex-shrink-0" /><span class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium">Soporte técnico especializado</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 border border-white/5"><CircleCheck class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-[#78BE20] flex-shrink-0" /><span class="text-white/90 text-sm font-medium">Tecnología de última generación</span></div></div><div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/10"><a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#78BE20] text-[#0F2E65] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#6aad1a] transition-colors">Solicitar propuesta<svg class="w-4 h-4">[Icon]</svg></a></div></div></div></div></section>
